You're supposed to say, "Where?"

90
00:10:08,185 --> 00:10:09,928
I don't want
to sing that dumb song.

91
00:10:10,395 --> 00:10:12,269
You don't have to sing.
Just say "Where?"

92
00:10:12,481 --> 00:10:13,595
All right. Where?

93
